net.nemerosa.ontrack.model.security

Interface GlobalFunction

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AccountGroupManagement, AccountManagement, ApplicationManagement, GlobalSettings, ProjectCreation, ProjectList

    public interface GlobalFunction
    Sub-interfaces define all functions available at application level. The list of available functions is available in the RolesService service and new functions can be contributed through extensions.
